Stuttgart Appoints New Coach
BONN , December 23 ( Xinhua ) -- German Ralf Rangnick has been named as coach of Bundesliga club VfB Stuttgart on July 1st 1999 , the club official said on Wednesday .
Rangnick , 40 , has won a promising reputation in German coaching circles and has led SSV Ulm , newly-promoted to the second division , to top spot .
He refused to move before next summer because of his desire to steer Ulm into Germany 's top flight .
